      "amount": "1 handful fresh"
    },
    {
      "name": "ginger powder",
      "amount": "1 tsp"
    },
    {
      "name": "bitter almonds",
      "amount": "1/4 cup, ground"
    },
    {
      "name": "flour",
      "amount": "3 tbsp"
    },
    {
      "name": "coconut oil",
      "amount": "2 tbsp melted"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "In a bowl, combine dates and wild garlic leaves. Add ginger powder and mix well.",
    "Stir in ground bitter almonds to the date mixture until evenly coated.",
    "Mix flour with coconut oil to create crumbs. Add the flour-coconut oil mixture into the date mixture and stir gently to distribute evenly.",
    "Transfer the crumbly mixture onto a greased baking dish, pressing down slightly for even distribution."
